These are lists of [[skyscraper]]s which are taller than {{convert|400|m|ft|abbr=on}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emporis.com/en/bu/sk/st/tp/wo/|title=World's Tallest Skyscrapers|publisher=''[[Emporis]]''|accessdate=28 May 2009}}</ref> [[Burj Khalifa]], in [[Dubai]] [[United Arab Emirates]], is the tallest building in the world since 4 January 2010 standing at {{convert|828|m|ft|abbr=on}}.
